data.description:
***Charming 3 Bedroom Home in the Heart of Bristol, TN***
Welcome to your future home in the picturesque Appalachian Highlands! This charming 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home on Cowan Street offers the perfect blend of comfort, modern amenities, and a fantastic location. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer, an aspiring Airbnb host, or looking to downsize, this delightful property has something for everyone.

As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The spacious living area is perfect for spending quality time with loved ones, and the newer appliances in the kitchen make meal preparation a breeze. The cozy dining area is ideal for family dinners and gatherings. The three bedrooms offer comfort and privacy, while the 1.5 bathrooms ensure convenience for all. With a newer heat pump, this home provides efficient climate control, making it an energy-efficient and cost-effective choice. 

The backyard is your own private oasis with a storage shed for your outdoor equipment and almost fully fenced for your privacy and peace of mind. Sit on your (9 x 22 ft) back, covered porch to enjoy the beautiful backyard. Whether you have kids or pets, they'll have a great space to play.

Cowan Street is situated in a friendly and welcoming neighborhood with access to great schools, perfect for families. If you're an outdoor enthusiast, you'll love the proximity to hiking trails in the Appalachian Highlands, offering endless opportunities for adventure and exploration. And, when it's time to indulge in some retail therapy or dine out, you're just a short drive away from shopping and dining options.

This charming Bristol home is not only move-in ready but offers endless possibilities for your future.. For under $200k, don't miss your chance to own this gem in Bristol, TN! Contact your Realtor to schedule a viewing and make this charming property your new home sweet home. Buyer/Buyer's Agent must verify all information within.
